<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Modern Database Query Interface</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6E8EFB, #7460EE);
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        select, button, input[type="submit"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        select option {
            color: black; /* Change the text color to black for options */
        }
        button, input[type="submit"] {
            background: #7460EE;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        button:hover, input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background: #5C50E6;
        }
        h2, h3 {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .db-holder {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .query-holder {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .results {
            margin-top: 30px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <form action="/process" id="form" method="POST">
        <h2>Query Selection Interface</h2>
        <div class="db-holder">
            <h3>Choose Your Database:</h3>
            <select id="database" name="database" required>
                <option value="" selected>Please select a database</option>
                <option value="sql">SQL</option>
                <option value="mongodb">MongoDB</option>
                <option value="neo4j">Neo4j</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        <div class="query-holder">
            <h3>Choose Your Query:</h3>
            <select id="query" name="query" required>
                <option value="" selected>Please select a query</option>
                <option value="1">1.What percentage of each race among patients</option>
                <option value="2">2.What is the ratio of males to females?</option>
                <option value="3">3.What is the distribution of race among patients for each admission type?</option>
                <option value="4">4.How does gender distribution vary across different discharge dispositions?</option>
                <option value="5">5.Among patients referred by physicians, clinics, or through emergency rooms, what is the racial breakdown?</option>
                <option value="6">6.Is there a significant difference in the admission source when comparing male and female patients?</option>
                <option value="7">7.For elective admissions, what is the breakdown of patients by race and gender?</option>
                <option value="8">8.Do outcomes for emergency room admissions differ significantly between male and female patients?</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    </form>
    <div class="results">
        <h3>The Query Results Will Shown In The New Window</h3>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
